#: ../../index.md:64
msgid "Welcome to pyMediaManager"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:66
msgid ""
"pyMediaManager (pyMM) is a Python-based media management application "
"designed to organize and manage large media collections with integrated "
"version control and plugin support."
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:69
msgid "Features"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:71
msgid "**100% Portable**: Run from USB/external drives with no installation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:72
msgid ""
"**Project Management**: Organize media files into structured projects "
"with templates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:73
msgid ""
"**Plugin System**: YAML manifest-based extensible architecture for "
"integrating external tools"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:74
msgid "**Git Integration**: Built-in version control with Git LFS support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:75
msgid ""
"**Cross-Platform**: Windows 10+, Linux, macOS with native USB drive "
"detection"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:76
msgid "**Modern UI**: Fluent Design with QFluentWidgets and PySide6"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:77
msgid "**Type-Safe**: Python 3.12+ with strict type hints and Pydantic validation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:78
#, python-format
msgid "**Well-Tested**: 193 tests with 73% code coverage"
msgstr ""

